		<hr />
		
		
			<div><strong>Video Lag/Frame Skipping issue</strong><br />&nbsp;</div>
		
		
		
		<div>This has only been a recent problem. Especially noticable in EQ, but I can also see it when moving my mouse... where every second on the dot my screen just locks for a split second, skipping a frame or two. This will go on for a few minutes, then stop, then come back a while later.<br />
<br />
I've ran Norton and Housecall - no viruses<br />
I've ran Spybot and Adaware - no spyware<br />
I ran my hard drive's diagnostic utility - no problems reported<br />
I uninstalled and reinstalled my graphics card - problem persists<br />
Task Manager processes so no unusual exe's running in the background, and when my screen freezes, my activity light on my CPU comes on.<br />
<br />
My last option is to reinstall XP, but I don't want to do that unless I can fix this another way.<br />
<br />
Danke~</div>
	</td>
</tr>
</table>
