		<hr />
		
		
		
		
		<div>Update #2!<br />
<br />
I went ahead and uninstalled the primary ide from the device manager, and let windows reinstall it on boot. Both say DMA now! *dance*<br />
<br />
I hope this solves my frame lag issue. Loading EQ to test it.<br />
<br />
Thank you Sneg.</div>
